 & =\frac{1}{2}\mu(\mbx)^{\top}\mu(\mbx)+C,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $C=-\log\g\mbSigma_{z}\g+Tr(\mbSigma_{z})-r$
\end_inset

 is a constant, which doesn't depend on 
